(9, 'An Ode To The Hanging Chair', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'an-ode-to-the-hanging-chair', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<span>Do you remember the <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\">perfect corner for reading</a>? Well, it looks like the hanging chairs become quite popular these days. I personally like it a lot (and based on the comments that I received  so do you) and I think that it will be great to have one in my home office. And usually these hanging chairs are outdoor furniture, but because the summer is ending why not just bring them inside. &nbsp;</span>\r\n\r\n<span>Im always happy to browse the new home-ware catalogue by <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">French Connection.</a> I found there some pretty amazing stuff and the style is always so recognizable. Probably none of us is surprised that the popular fashion brand also created a pretty fall home collection, because we all know there is a tight connection between the trends in the fashion and those of the interiors. &nbsp;</span>\r\n\r\n<span>The new autumn catalogue is <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">different this time</a>. It is much darker, relies on the earth natural tones and make the home to look cozier. <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">Two years ago for example</a> everything was white and light.&nbsp;Unfortunately they&nbsp;</span>', '2017-10-25 22:30:16', '2022-09-08 06:33:13', '2017-10-25 17:00:00', 1, 1, 0, 'magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-02.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-02_1.jpg;magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-02b.jpg;magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-02c.jpg', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 0),
(10, 'Australian Home in Natural Tones', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'australian-home-in-natural-tones', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>I decided to step away for a while from my daily routine of searching for furniture, textiles and accessories for my new home and to find a little inspiration in somebody else&rsquo;s beautiful home. What do you think about this house in Australia in natural tones? I love how everything here is combined in a natural color palette. Even the flowers everywhere are selected carefully to be white with dark green leaves and to complement and fill the variability of the textures. This gorgeous pictures were taken by the talented Sharyn Cairns for Vogue Living, Australia. <img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/Blog/unlimited-blog-home-03a.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/Blog/unlimited-blog-home-03c.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>', '2017-10-26 01:01:36', '2022-09-08 06:33:13', '2017-10-25 17:00:00', 1, 1, 0, 'magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-03.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'I decided to step away for a while from my daily routine of searching for furniture.', 0),
(11, 'Cozy home with natural details and industrial touch', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'cozy-home-with-natural-details-and-industrial-touch', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The home of stylist and photographer Daniella Witt is wonderful and very inspiring, just like everything that Daniella does. The color palette is not very rich, but selected in a way to enhance the feeling of comfort and softness &ndash; black, white and lots of gray. And when you add it to the natural texture of wood, quality textiles and industrial touch, according to my opinion you will have an interesting and lovely home. More photos you can see here. <img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/Blog/unlimited-blog-home-04a.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /> <img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/Blog/unlimited-blog-home-04b.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" /></p>', '2017-10-26 02:09:09', '2022-09-08 06:33:13', '2017-10-25 17:00:00', 1, 1, 0, 'magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-04.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'The home of stylist and photographer Daniella Witt is wonderful and very inspiring, just like everything that Daniella does', 0),
(12, 'a Notebook collection with inspiring quotes and our winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'a-notebook-collection-with-inspiring-quotes-and-our-winner', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The amazing Lotta Agaton styled these pictures for Therese Sennerholt and her wonderful new collection of notebook. And since I just adore inspirational quotes I just had to mention it here.\r\n \r\nAnd by the way we have a winner! To the giveaway of 79ideas and Amy Waltz Design. And the winner is Ira Vikstrm. Congratulations to her and many thanks to Amy.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/Blog/unlimited-blog-home-05a.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"\" />', '2017-10-26 02:22:49', '2022-09-08 06:33:13', '2017-10-25 17:00:00', 1, 1, 0, 'magefan_blog/unlimited-blog-home-05.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'The amazing Lotta Agaton styled these pictures for Therese Sennerholt and her wonderful new collection of notebook.', 0),
(13, 'How To Wear White Sneakers For Men', 'How To Wear White Sneakers For Men', 'How To Wear White Sneakers For Men', 'How To Wear White Sneakers For Men', 'how-to-wear-white-sneakers-for-men', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino;\">I am a huge on wearing white sneakers, and I wear them with almost all kind of outfits. Yes, I do get comments sometimes that \"how can you wear sneakers with a blazer\" and my response invariably is, you can wear your white sneakers with a blazer or even with a full blown suit for that matter. If I am not mistaking, I at least own 7 pairs of white sneakers. (Yeah, that\'s how much I love them) I just can\'t hold myself back when I spot a pair of good white sneakers, online or in store. Almost always I end up buying it.</span></em></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino;\"><br /></span></em></p>\r\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large; font-family: \'book antiqua\', palatino;\"><br /></span></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-24\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Sure my shoe wardrobe is bit too much white right now, but I am not complaining.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Oh, and yes I do not own a single pair of dress shoes (oxfords, brogues, monks) nothing, nada, zero. Not that I don\'t appreciate a pair of top quality dress shoes, but I think I am not cut out for that kind of super formal dressing.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">I like to keep my outfits comfortable, casual and mostly simple. There\'s a huge misconception about white sneakers is that you can only wear them with jeans &amp; t-shirt outfits. And that is so wrong.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">I have friends who often ask me, why the hell are you wearing sneakers with chinos + blazer outfit? And my first reaction is \"do they look bad\" and their reply is almost NO every single time.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 space-md\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/main-content-04/blog-02.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"blog-02.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-24 space-md\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">So, if my outfit is not looking bad (In fact it\'s looking super edgy and sharp), why shouldn\'t I wear my white sneakers. right?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Now, I see a lot of street style bloggers wearing white sneakers with almost all kind of outfits. But there\'s a large group of men that still thinks white sneakers are only for sports or casual settings.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-24\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 space-md\"><img src=\"{{media url=\"wysiwyg/codazon/main-content-04/blog-03.jpg\"}}\" alt=\"blog-03.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Now, to prove that you can wear your white sneakers with almost all kind of outfits, I have curated 9 sharp looks from Bernd Hower\'s (Insta Celebrity and Fashion &amp; Lifestyle blogger) Instagram page.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">If you are into white sneakers, then you gotta follow this guy on Instagram. His Instagram account is all about casual, semi-formal, business casual outfits. And one thing you can\'t miss that Bernd is a huge fan of white sneakers like you and me.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Ready to see some cool outfit ideas? alright, let\'s dive in.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2018-01-01 21:07:19', '2022-09-08 06:33:13', '2018-01-01 17:00:00', 1, 1, 0, 'magefan_blog/menfashion-blog-01.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '6', NULL, NULL, '2018-01-01', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '<p>I am a huge on wearing white sneakers, and I wear them with almost all kind of outfits. Yes, I do get comments sometimes that \"how can you wear sneakers with a blazer\" and my response invariably is, you can wear your white sneakers with a blazer or even with a full blown suit for that matter. If I am not mistaking, I at least own 7 pairs of white sneakers. (Yeah, that\'s how much I love them) I just can\'t hold myself back when I spot a pair of good white sneakers, online or in store. Almost always I end up buying it.</p>', 0);
