(90, 'Grilled Pineapple-Ancho Margarita', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'grilled-pineapple-ancho-margarita', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Oversized sunglasses took the world by storm when they first entered the fashion sphere. There were critics and admirers, but after remaining relevant for over a decade, its clear that the critics have had no influence on the popularity of oversized shades. Although their popularity has remained constant, one thing has surely not: their size. Oversized sunnies have only become more oversized throughout the years. The Dior SoLight collection is proof of that.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>The Dior SoLight 1</h2>\r\n<p>The first pair of sunglasses in the collection, the Dior SoLight1, take the wide frame, large lens look took an extreme. And, all we have to say is that we are all for pushing limits. These trendy shades have a unique mask effect, therefore, if you need a big pair of shades to protect you from the sun, cover your face after one too many long nights, or both, the SoLight1 are calling your name. These sunglasses are super lightweight and have lenses that offer 100% UVA/UVB protection. Thankfully, we carry them in not one, but three colors: black frames with dark gray lenses,ivory frames with nude lenses and light pink frame&nbsp;with light pink lenses to match.</p>\r\n<h2>The Dior SoLight 2</h2>\r\n<p>The Dior SoLight2 sunglasses are a rectangular take on the oversized frame style. These chunky sunnies have an ultra-thin, curved frame, which makes them large and in charge, yet super light. Their monochromatic lenses also offer 100% UVA/UVB protection, so they are just as trendy and shielding as their SoLight1 counterpart. They come in four different colors: light pink frames with matching lenses, dark blue frames with matching lenses, black frames with shaded grey lenses&nbsp; and brown frames with shaded brown lenses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Its Time to Shop</h2>\r\n<p>So, how much more do you need to understand that you NEED a pair of oversized sunnies and that Dior has seriously got your back.</p>', '2021-11-29 21:12:24', '2022-09-08 06:33:14', '2021-10-15 00:00:00', 1, 1, 0, 'magefan_blog/wine1.jpg', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '<p>Ancho Reyes is a Mexican liqueur made from Ancho and Poblano peppers. It is a sweet and subtly spiced with a hint of smokiness. Ancho Reyes liqueur adds a great lift to many traditional cocktails and works particularly well in Margaritas.</p>', 0),
